    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a standard of preservation typically reserved for private collections. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine cabin appointments, confirms a history of meticulous stewardship. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
