    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This investment-grade A80 Toyota Supra Turbo features the iconic 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six paired with the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The powertrain remains in factory-spec synchronization, exhibiting pristine compression across all cylinders and a leak-free vacuum system. The Torsen limited-slip differential and double-wishbone suspension are fully sorted, providing the precise handling characteristics expected from a showroom-caliber vehicle. With all original VIN tags present and no signs of heat-cycle degradation on the wiring harness or vacuum lines, this is a mechanically flawless example for the discerning collector.",
